In the Matter of PHILIP GROSS HARDWARE & SUPPLY CO., Bankrupt. GROSS v. MILWAUKEE DOWNTOWN SHOPPING NEWS, Inc. No. 5413. Circuit Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. May 27, 1935.

Before EVANS, SPARKS, and FITZHENRY, Circuit Judges.

Alexander W. Schütz, of Milwaukee, Wis., for appellant. Morris Karon, of Milwaukee, Wis., John C. Love, of Waukesha, Wis., and Walter L. Gold, of Milwaukee, Wis., for appellee. PER CURIAM.

It is now here ordered, adjudged, and decreed by this court that the order or decree of the District Court of the United States for the Eastern District of Wisconsin in this cause appealed from be, and the same is hereby, affirmed, with costs.
